author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Magellan Financial Group ‍Posts HY Net Operating Profit Of $53.5 Mln
text:
Feb 6 (Reuters) - Magellan Financial Group Ltd:
* ‍HY TOTAL REVENUE UP BY 27.5% TO $195.8 MILLION​ * ‍INTERIM DIVIDEND OF 44.5 CENTS PER SECURITY​ * HY NET OPERATING PROFIT $53.5 MILLION VERSUS $87.0 MILLION
* ‍EXPECT GROUP‘S MARKETING EXPENSE TO INCREASE MATERIALLY IN 2018 FINANCIAL YEAR TO ABOUT $11.0-11.5 MILLION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
